About the never the same colour thing. It was because older tv's often lost sync with the colour carrier. (or something like that) Newer tv's are alot better at this but can stil sometimes lose the signal (in theory) But its definitly true. (pal fixes this by rotating the colour carrier 180 degrees every frame (or was it line?) )<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3369">Jeroen</a> — Fri Mar 27, 2009 1:57 pm</p><hr />
